{"tid":1964663,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"CS1.6喪屍場，你玩過邊種mode","createTime":"2020-04-09T03:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T12:39:24.000Z","uid":295532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"449d01a1df40a21ad52d4922e1e884069ecfd22b","tid":1964663,"uid":295532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T03:50:17.000Z","msg":"話說之前有ching講過cs1.6，我自己好鍾意玩喪屍場，唔知有冇同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次喺個叫無名氏嘅server，係最早期喪屍。冇技能，得血多，只係個揸刀嘅喪屍，個樣係無頭嘅科學家白袍血漬造型<br />\n<br />\n之後就到bb server，打啲類似異型嘅野，個時有技能點，35 lv，輕功防護加乘。啲adm係變型金剛造型，有得用繩飛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到香港喪屍server，儲字彈包買物品，飛行器火箭炮不得了。喪屍技能多樣化，有傳統技能、有噴口水、飛行、小型喪屍；但冇咗lv up呢樣野。但個時初中識到唔少adm，暑假一齊喺屋企連線捉cheater<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後期就係l4d興起，技能同槍都有好大變化，黃金獵手，獵戶座，銀色嘅神狙記到而家，傷害最高。<br />\n<br />\n最後就係re系列，有幾個版本，但都係可以揀職業，最多三個聖戰士神槍手醫療兵呢啲又係好正，個時Awp同連射散彈都好屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後兩期l4d同re多咗好多模式，魔王逃走英雄等等都有，記憶都有啲亂，而且好多server都有出過，所以記錯唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但真係好好玩，以前server滿咗，要喺msn叫啲adm加我入去。一齊打喪屍個陣大家都好興奮。尋日入返cs1.6睇，啲人冇晒，啲server死晒，真心sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d49a0a6cbff75ba81cc2737578277def6170e6b","tid":1964663,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T03:52:18.000Z","msg":"JailBreak"},{"pid":"df34d797fa3420cc1b55cad7ebbbe56ad583fb83","tid":1964663,"uid":99607,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T03:54:59.000Z","msg":"warcraft mode最好玩 夜精 刀仔隱形<br />\n喪屍mode 呢D聽到都覺得低能<br />\n同cso一樣咁on9"},{"pid":"e5ddb8a9512a8ff6bd7adef091ede2447acaf650","tid":1964663,"uid":295532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df34d797fa3420cc1b55cad7ebbbe56ad583fb83","tid":1964663,"uid":99607,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T03:54:59.000Z","msg":"warcraft mode最好玩 夜精 刀仔隱形<br />\n喪屍mode 呢D聽到都覺得低能<br />\n同cso一樣咁on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T03:56:54.000Z","msg":"喪屍場講team work喎，而且你魔獸啲角色，後期都有加入去"},{"pid":"d44c9d532828bcb789ebf235066e454612454f3e","tid":1964663,"uid":155781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:54:33.000Z","msg":"TIG FXG TD CTP 喪屍場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa724f7e1ebd803bc4102a602a1b06e48482669","tid":1964663,"uid":174441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:23:07.000Z","msg":"TiG"},{"pid":"1e50b666a5f948f4eb3b5204b3c3e33edbbb12e7","tid":1964663,"uid":295532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d44c9d532828bcb789ebf235066e454612454f3e","tid":1964663,"uid":155781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:54:33.000Z","msg":"TIG FXG TD CTP 喪屍場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T10:53:21.000Z","msg":"唔太記得，tig把awp係咪藍狙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44eef04dbdad1b9339b9c9cabcbd60c63ff6aef7","tid":1964663,"uid":155781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e50b666a5f948f4eb3b5204b3c3e33edbbb12e7","tid":1964663,"uid":295532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d44c9d532828bcb789ebf235066e454612454f3e","tid":1964663,"uid":155781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:54:33.000Z","msg":"TIG FXG TD CTP 喪屍場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T10:53:2